都扮識。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連之前日日鬧港鐵嘅黎廣德都睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1264b0c6ef75641624763e0b2b55e5ed8521bacf","tid":782700,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T01:15:06.000Z","msg":"唔影響行車安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12eb63f2d52c0380aef7047e4439350bee847ed","tid":782700,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"發覺香港日日都有大事 但依家好似唔洗問責無人會比坐監咁 日日有新野 過幾日舊事就提都無人提"}]}